that the dog somehow

00:03:26.700 --> 00:03:28.480
will know how to
log onto a computer.

00:03:28.480 --> 00:03:30.700
This is probably
an impossibility.

00:03:30.700 --> 00:03:33.810
And then, actually, be
able to read something

00:03:33.810 --> 00:03:36.960
on a website, type on a website,
and then read on a website?

00:03:36.960 --> 00:03:39.240
This seems close to an
impossibility, if not

00:03:39.240 --> 00:03:40.450
