00:03:44.870 --> 00:03:46.790
This seems pretty
close to impossible.

00:03:46.790 --> 00:03:49.940
So this probability is
pretty darn close to 0.

00:03:49.940 --> 00:03:51.620
If it's impossible,
it would be 0,

00:03:51.620 --> 00:03:55.710
but it'd be much, much
closer to 0 than 0.01.

00:03:55.710 --> 00:04:00.610
This is a small probability,
but this is not super unlikely.

00:04:00.610 --> 00:04:03.890
If this was the case, this means
that if we had 100 realities

00:04:03.890 --> 00:04:07.090
